            {% for line in object.pledge.person.full_address() %}
            {{ line }}{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
        {% endif %}
        </p>
        <p>Dear 
{% if object.overwrite_name %}{{ object.overwrite_name }}{% elif object.pledge.person.name %}{{ object.pledge.person.name }}{% else %}{{ object.pledge.person.initiated_name }}{% endif %},</p>

<p>Please accept our humble obeisances. All glories to Srila Prabhupada!</p>

<p>We at the North American TOVP Office wish to give you our heartfelt thanks
for your contribution towards the construction of the glorious Temple of the
Vedic Planetarium in Mayapur Dham, helping to spread the mercy of Sri
Caitanya Mahaprabhu and Srila Prabhupada. This project is their vision and
prophecy, and you have become part of a great historic and significant event
that will transform the world for thousands of years to come. We pray the
Lord blesses you with peace, health, prosperity, and His divine love!</p>


<p>"The Supreme Lord is situated in everyone's heart, O Arjuna, and is
directing the wanderings of all living entities, who are seated as on a
machine, made of the material energy. O scion of Bharata, surrender unto Him
utterly. By His grace you will attain transcendental peace and the supreme
and eternal abode." Bhagavad-gita 18.61-62</p>

<p>You have donated <ContributionLastAmount>. No goods or services were
provided in exchange for the donation. Your donation is fully tax deductible
on your (USA) Federal Income Tax Return.</p>

<p>We look forward to your continued support and pray this finds you in good
health and peaceful mood. Hare Krishna.</p>

<p>Sincerely,</p>

<p>Yours in the Service of the TOVP</p>

<p>Vraja Vilasa das</p>

<p>Global Director of Fundraising, TOVP</p>
    </div>




